reviewText: Ok well this is a lengthy disc of Street Fury footage, that is pretty cool.  There are two or three chapters' worth of the girls, that is also cool.  There are lots of flashes of boobs and nipples, that is hot.  There are flashes of coochie that are CENSORED WITH WHITE BLOTS, that is NOT NOT NOT HOT.  You F'ing guys. You also have "Uncut photo shoots" listed in the features on the back - "you keep using that word... I do not think it means what you think it means."  Anyway, if you have to censor it like that, then what is the point of showing it at all?  And a lot of the nudity is intercut with the dude's face up close to the camera, again what the hell are you thinking??  Some of the white blots are to cover up when a girl is dancing around and merely wearing a very short skirt and no underwear, some of the white blots cover up what shows through the see-through underwear, some of the white blots cover up when a girl is actually pulling the panties aside and tugging the lips upward, like really trying to show her hoo ha.  But trust me, the white blobs are large and you will not see anything.  WTF.  Without those stupid censor blots, this would been a 5-star rating easy, and it breaks my heart to think of how sweetly awesomely sexy this could have been.  What a waste of potential, shame on you for ruining such beautiful footage!!
